  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/16/google-play-paypal/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/c36b769af8a37aa710d01fd362711e0/paypal-steveganz-flickr.jpg\" style=\"height: 339px; width: 620px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\nGoogle 今天正式宣布，从现在开始用户将可以通过 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/paypal\">PayPal</a> 来完成应用、游戏、电子书等内容的支付，让使用者在信用卡、礼品卡、运营商代扣等方式之外再多一种选择。不过需要注意的是，PayPal 的购买范围并不包括实体产品，所以要想买手机之类东西的话还是要用老方法才行呢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/05/15/google-play-paypal/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.droid-life.com/2014/05/15/paypal-finally-becomes-a-payment-option-in-google-play/\" target=\"_blank\">Droid Life</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://android-developers.blogspot.ca/2014/05/helping-you-go-global-with-more.html\" target=\"_blank\">Android Developers Blog</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/16/google-play-paypal/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20886979/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/16/google-play-paypal/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
